Greetings,

This is a LeafsTV Interactive plugin for XBMC. Just add your login
information in the plugin settings and you should be set to watch live
and archived games.

If you have any trouble (especially with archived game) please confirm
that they work in teh web UI as the frequently do not. Otherwise, if
you think you have found a legit bug, please email me at
micahgalizia@gmail.com